        "description": "Gesture VR is a drawing app with an emphasis on figure drawing. Draw in 2D or 3D from over 200 high-quality models (more to come!) and get complete control of the lights, timers, and poses. Practice alone or group up with friends!\n\n~Features~\n\n• Draw in 2D or 3D\n• Draw on real paper with passthrough!\n• Complete control over the light angle and pose duration\n• Group up with friends and draw together!\n• Draw your way with adjustable pen positioning found in the settings. \n• Over 200 models, including some animals and fantasy creatures.\n• Scale and rotate the drawing pad \n• Choose between 3 studio environments + passthrough\n• Turn on and off nudity \n• Support for Left and Right handed artists!\n• Capture and export your favourite 2D sketches\n\nSketches can be found here:\n(Android\\data\\com.NickLaddVrArtandAnimation.GestureVR\\files\\Images)",
